00:24:14.980 --> 00:24:18.760
So white reflector,
not even diffuser.

00:24:18.760 --> 00:24:21.540
And Kyrill is going to
hold it from other side.

00:24:21.540 --> 00:24:25.180
Make it vertical and closer.

00:24:25.180 --> 00:24:25.940
Awesome.

